  :root { --w: 8.5in; --h: 11in; }
  html,body { margin:0; background:#ececec; font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; }
  .shell { max-width: calc(var(--w) + 1in); margin: 16px auto; padding: 12px; }
  .toolbar { display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .toolbar input[type="text"] { width: 220px; }
  .btn { padding:10px 16px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; }
  .pages { display:grid; gap:18px; }
  .page { width:var(--w); height:var(--h); position:relative; margin:0 auto; background:#fff; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.25); overflow:hidden; }
  .bg { position:absolute; inset:0; background-repeat:no-repeat; background-position:center top; background-size:cover; }
  .field { position:absolute; font-size:12pt; padding:2px 4px; border:1px solid #999; background:rgba(255,255,255,.85); outline:none;  text-align:center;}
  .muted { opacity:.85; font-size:.9rem; }
  @page { size: Letter; margin: 0.5in; }

<div class="shell">
  <div class="toolbar">
    <label>VIN</label><input id="vinInput" type="text" maxlength="30">
    <label>Make</label><input id="makeInput" type="text" maxlength="30">
    <label>Model</label><input id="modelInput" type="text" maxlength="30">
  </div>
  <div class="toolbar">
    <label>Year</label><input id="yearInput" type="text" maxlength="10">
    <label>Stock</label><input id="stockInput" type="text" maxlength="20">
    <button class="btn" id="savePdf">Save PDF</button>
    <span class="muted">Prefill: ?vin=...&make=...&model=...&year=...&stock=...</span>
  </div>

  <div class="pages">
    <div class="page" id="page1">
      <div class="bg" id="bg1"></div>
      <input id="VIN"   class="field" style="top:1.84in;left:5.35in;width:2.05in" placeholder="VIN">
      <input id="MAKE"  class="field" style="top:1.84in;left:1.00in;width:1.25in" placeholder="Make">
      <input id="MODEL" class="field" style="top:1.84in;left:2.36in;width:1.31in" placeholder="Model">
      <input id="YEAR"  class="field" style="top:1.84in;left:3.78in;width:0.40in" placeholder="Year">
      <input id="STOCK" class="field" style="top:1.84in;left:4.29in;width:0.95in" placeholder="Stock">
    </div>
    <div class="page" id="page2">
      <div class="bg" id="bg2"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jspdf@2.5.1/dist/jspdf.umd.min.js"></script>
<script>
const POS = {
  VIN:   { top: 1.84, left: 5.45, width: 2.25 },
  MAKE:  { top: 1.84, left: 1.00, width: 1.25 },
  MODEL: { top: 1.84, left: 2.36, width: 1.31 },
  YEAR:  { top: 1.84, left: 3.78, width: 0.45 },
  STOCK: { top: 1.84, left: 4.31, width: 1.00 }
};

const PAGE_W_IN = 8.5, PAGE_H_IN = 11.0;
const FONT_SIZE_PT = 12;
const BASELINE_ADJ_IN = 0.16;

const page1Data = "data:image/png;base64,";
const page2Data = "data:image/png;base64,";

document.getElementById('bg1').style.backgroundImage = 'url("'+page1Data+'")';
document.getElementById('bg2').style.backgroundImage = 'url("'+page2Data+'")';

const map = [
  ['vinInput','VIN'],
  ['makeInput','MAKE'],
  ['modelInput','MODEL'],
  ['yearInput','YEAR'],
  ['stockInput','STOCK']
];
for (const [inputId, fieldId] of map) {
  const i = document.getElementById(inputId);
  const f = document.getElementById(fieldId);
  i.addEventListener('input', () => f.value = i.value);
}

(function prefill() {
  const q = new URLSearchParams(location.search);
  for (const [inputId, fieldId] of map) {
    const key = inputId.replace('Input','').toLowerCase();
    const v = q.get(key);
    if (v) {
      document.getElementById(inputId).value = v;
      document.getElementById(fieldId).value = v;
    }
  }
})();

function drawText(doc, txt, pos) {
  if (!txt) return;
  doc.setFontSize(FONT_SIZE_PT);
  doc.setTextColor(0,0,0);
  doc.setFont('helvetica','normal');
  const lines = doc.splitTextToSize(txt, pos.width);
  doc.text(lines, pos.left + pos.width/2, pos.top + BASELINE_ADJ_IN, { align: "center" });
}

async function savePdf() {
  const { jsPDF } = window.jspdf;
  const doc = new jsPDF({ unit:'in', format:'letter', compress:true });
  doc.addImage(page1Data, 'PNG', 0, 0, PAGE_W_IN, PAGE_H_IN);
  drawText(doc, document.getElementById('VIN').value,   POS.VIN);
  drawText(doc, document.getElementById('MAKE').value,  POS.MAKE);
  drawText(doc, document.getElementById('MODEL').value, POS.MODEL);
  drawText(doc, document.getElementById('YEAR').value,  POS.YEAR);
  drawText(doc, document.getElementById('STOCK').value, POS.STOCK);
  doc.addPage('letter', 'portrait');
  doc.addImage(page2Data, 'PNG', 0, 0, PAGE_W_IN, PAGE_H_IN);
  doc.save('Buyers_Guide_filled.pdf');
}

document.getElementById('savePdf').addEventListener('click', () => savePdf().catch(e => alert('PDF generation failed: ' + e.message)));
</script>

<script>
(function(){
  function g(id){return document.getElementById(id)}
  function setPair(inputId, fieldId, v){ if(v==null) return; var i=g(inputId), f=g(fieldId); if(i && !i.value) i.value=v; if(f && !f.value) f.value=v; }
  function setPairForce(inputId, fieldId, v){ if(v==null) return; var i=g(inputId), f=g(fieldId); if(i) i.value=v; if(f) f.value=v; }
  var q=new URLSearchParams(location.search);
  var vin=q.get("vin"); var make=q.get("make"); var model=q.get("model"); var year=q.get("year"); var stock=q.get("stock");
  if(vin){ setPairForce("vinInput","VIN",vin); }
  if(make){ setPairForce("makeInput","MAKE",make); }
  if(model){ setPairForce("modelInput","MODEL",model); }
  if(year){ setPairForce("yearInput","YEAR",year); }
  if(stock){ setPairForce("stockInput","STOCK",stock); }
  if(!vin) return;
  var url="https://vpic.nhtsa.dot.gov/api/vehicles/decodevinvaluesextended/"+encodeURIComponent(vin)+"?format=json";
  fetch(url).then(function(r){return r.json()}).then(function(j){
    var r=(j&&j.Results&&j.Results[0])?j.Results[0]:null;
    if(!r) return;
    if(!make) setPair("makeInput","MAKE",r.Make);
    if(!model) setPair("modelInput","MODEL",r.Model);
    if(!year) setPair("yearInput","YEAR",r.ModelYear);
  }).catch(function(){});
})();
</script>


<script>
(function(){
  var vinEl = document.getElementById('vinInput');
  var makeEl = document.getElementById('makeInput');
  var modelEl = document.getElementById('modelInput');
  var yearEl = document.getElementById('yearInput');
  function up(s){ return (s||"").toString().trim().toUpperCase(); }
  var t=null;
  function fetchVIN(v){
    var u="https://vpic.nhtsa.dot.gov/api/vehicles/decodevinvaluesextended/"+encodeURIComponent(up(v))+"?format=json";
    fetch(u).then(function(r){return r.json()}).then(function(j){
      var r=(j&&j.Results&&j.Results[0])?j.Results[0]:null;
      if(!r) return;
      if(!makeEl.value && r.Make)  { makeEl.value  = r.Make;  var f=document.getElementById('MAKE');  if(f) f.value  = r.Make; }
      if(!modelEl.value && r.Model){ modelEl.value = r.Model; var f2=document.getElementById('MODEL'); if(f2) f2.value = r.Model; }
      if(!yearEl.value && r.ModelYear){ yearEl.value = r.ModelYear; var f3=document.getElementById('YEAR'); if(f3) f3.value = r.ModelYear; }
    }).catch(function(){});
  }
  if (vinEl){
    vinEl.addEventListener('input', function(){
      var v = up(vinEl.value).replace(/[^0-9A-Z]/g,'');
      if (v.length === 17){
        clearTimeout(t);
        t = setTimeout(function(){ fetchVIN(v); }, 400);
      }
    });
  }
})();
</script>


<script>
(function(){
  var q=new URLSearchParams(location.search);
  var hasParams=!!(q.get("vin")||q.get("make")||q.get("model")||q.get("year")||q.get("stock"));
  if(!hasParams) return;
  try{
    var sh=document.querySelector(".shell"); if(sh) sh.style.display="none";
    document.documentElement.style.background="#fff"; document.body.style.background="#fff";
  }catch(e){}
  function ready(){
    var v=document.getElementById("VIN"), m=document.getElementById("MAKE"), d=document.getElementById("MODEL"), y=document.getElementById("YEAR");
    return v&&v.value && ((m&&m.value)||(d&&d.value)||(y&&y.value));
  }
  var t0=Date.now(), max=3500;
  (function wait(){
    if(ready()||Date.now()-t0>max){ try{ savePdf(); }catch(e){ alert("PDF generation failed: "+e.message); } }
    else{ setTimeout(wait,120); }
  })();
})();
</script>
</body>
</html>
